 Hut is promoting their new big sliders

00:00:11.912 --> 00:00:15.952
and instantly I thought, " I could put that on 
 a portobello mushroom and it would be so good."

00:00:15.952 --> 00:00:20.178
So that is what we will be doing today. Let's get started.

00:00:20.178 --> 00:00:25.392
Start by setting your oven to broil. I put mine on high, but 
 you know whatever high is on your oven, set it to that."

00:00:25.392 --> 00:00:29.663
Next we are going to clean our mushrooms with a wet paper towel.

00:00:29.663 --> 00:00:33.901
I am just going to wipe off the outside. I am going 
 to take the remainder of the stem out and 

00:00:33.901 --> 00:00:38.939
